{"route":{"route":"/posts/c7816edc/","outputPath":"posts/c7816edc/index.html","kind":"post","title":"golang socks5/http proxy","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"c7816edc"}},"description":"完整实现代码: socks5 client socks5 server http server 此处已socks5client为例,大致流程都相同,只是协议不同: socks5运行流程如下: tcp: 本机和代理服务端协商和建立连接； 本机告诉代理服务端目标服务的地址； 代理服务端去连接目标服务，成功后告诉本机； 本机","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/golang socks5⁄http server.md","route":"/posts/c7816edc/","abbrlink":"c7816edc","title":"golang socks5/http proxy","date":"2019-03-06 20:02:47","updated":"2020-05-30 00:00:00","tags":["socks5","golang"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<p>完整实现代码:<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Asutorufa/yuhaiin/blob/master/net/proxy/socks5/client/socks5client.go\">socks5 client</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Asutorufa/yuhaiin/blob/master/net/proxy/socks5/server/server.go\">socks5 server</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Asutorufa/yuhaiin/blob/master/net/proxy/http/server/server.go\">http server</a></p>\n<p>此处已socks5client为例,大致流程都相同,只是协议不同:</p>\n<p>socks5运行流程如下:</p>\n<p>tcp:<br>\n- 本机和代理服务端协商和建立连接；<br>\n- 本机告诉代理服务端目标服务的地址；<br>\n- 代理服务端去连接目标服务，成功后告诉本机；<br>\n- 本机开始发送原本应发送到目标服务的数据给代理服务端，由代理服务端完成数据转发。<br>\nudp:<br>\n- udp因为是无连接的,所以所以数据一次只用一个udp包<br>\n- socks5是通过tcp先确认socks5 server支持udp,然后再通过udp发送请求</p>\n<h2 id=\"先进行tcp连接\">先进行TCP连接</h2>\n<p>golang实现(<em>这里的地址我是本地socks5服务端</em>)</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">conn,err := net.Dial(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;tcp&quot;</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;127.0.0.1:1080&quot;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    fmt.Println(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"向socks5服务端发送验证\">向socks5服务端发送验证</h2>\n<p>验证字段:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">VER</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">NMETHODS</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">METHODS</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1字节</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1字节</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1-255字节</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n<li>VER是SOCKS版本，这里应该是0x05；</li>\n<li>NMETHODS是METHODS部分的长度；</li>\n<li>METHODS是客户端支持的认证方式列表，每个方法占1字节。当前的定义是：\n<ul>\n<li>0x00 不需要认证</li>\n<li>0x01 GSSAPI</li>\n<li>0x02 用户名、密码认证</li>\n<li>0x03 - 0x7F由IANA分配（保留）</li>\n<li>0x80 - 0xFE为私人方法保留</li>\n<li>0xFF 无可接受的方法</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>golang实现代码:</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">sendData := []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>{<span class=\"hljs-number\">0x05</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x01</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x00</span>}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> _, err := conn.Write(sendData); err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> err</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">getData := <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">make</span>([]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> _, err = conn.Read(getData[:]); err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> err</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> getData[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>] != <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x05</span> || getData[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0xFF</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> errors.New(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;socks5 first handshake failed!&quot;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> getData[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x02</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    sendData := <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">append</span>(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">append</span>(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">append</span>(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">                []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>{<span class=\"hljs-number\">0x01</span>, <span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(socks5client.Username))},</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">                []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>(socks5client.Username)...),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">            <span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(socks5client.Password))),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>(socks5client.Password)...)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    _, _ = conn.Write(sendData)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    getData := <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">make</span>([]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> _, err = conn.Read(getData[:]); err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> err</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> getData[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x01</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">26</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> errors.New(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;username or password not correct,socks5 handshake failed!&quot;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">27</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">28</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"向socks5服务端发送请求\">向socks5服务端发送请求</h2>\n<p>请求字段:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">VER</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">CMD</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">RSV</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">ATYP</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">DST.ADDR</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">DST.PORT</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1字节</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1字节</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">0x00</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1字节</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">动态</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">2字节</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ul>\n<li>VER是SOCKS版本，这里应该是0x05；</li>\n<li>CMD是SOCK的命令码\n<ul>\n<li>0x01表示CONNECT请求</li>\n<li>0x02表示BIND请求</li>\n<li>0x03表示UDP转发</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>RSV 0x00，保留</li>\n<li>ATYP DST.ADDR类型\n<ul>\n<li>0x01 IPv4地址，DST.ADDR部分4字节长度</li>\n<li>0x03 域名，DST.ADDR部分第一个字节为域名长度，DST.ADDR剩余的内容为域名，没有\\0结尾。</li>\n<li>0x04 IPv6地址，16个字节长度。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>DST.ADDR 目的地址</li>\n<li>DST.PORT 网络字节序表示的目的端口</li>\n</ul>\n<p>golang实现代码</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 此处为向 www.google.com:443 发送请求</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">domain := <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;www.google.com&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">serverPort := <span class=\"hljs-number\">443</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">sendData = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">append</span>(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">append</span>(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>{<span class=\"hljs-number\">0x5</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x01</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x00</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x03</span>, <span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">len</span>(domain))},</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">        []<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>(domain)...), <span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>(serverPort&gt;&gt;<span class=\"hljs-number\">8</span>),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>(serverPort&amp;<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>))</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> _,err = conn.Write(sendData); err!=<span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    fmt.Println(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">getData := <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">make</span>([]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1024</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> _, err = conn.Read(getData[:]); err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> err</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> getData[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>] != <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x05</span> || getData[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] != <span class=\"hljs-number\">0x00</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> errors.New(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;socks5 second handshake failed!&quot;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"进行数据转发\">进行数据转发</h2>\n<p>golang实现代码(<em>不太熟悉各种请求这里随便弄了一个</em>)</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> _,err = conn.Write([]<span class=\"hljs-type\">byte</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;GET /generate_204/ HTTP/2.0\\r\\n&quot;</span>)); err!=<span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>{</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    fmt.Println(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"关闭tcp连接\">关闭TCP连接</h2>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">conn.Close()</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"udp\">UDP</h2>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">      +----+------+------+----------+----------+----------+</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      |RSV | FRAG | ATYP | DST.ADDR | DST.PORT |   DATA   |</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      +----+------+------+----------+----------+----------+</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      | 2  |  1   |  1   | Variable |    2     | Variable |</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">      +----+------+------+----------+----------+----------+</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">     The fields in the UDP request header are:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-code\">          o  RSV  Reserved X&#x27;0000&#x27;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">          o  FRAG    Current fragment number</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">          o  ATYP    address type of following addresses:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">             o  IP V4 address: X&#x27;01&#x27;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">             o  DOMAINNAME: X&#x27;03&#x27;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">             o  IP V6 address: X&#x27;04&#x27;</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">          o  DST.ADDR       desired destination address</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">          o  DST.PORT       desired destination port</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">          o  DATA     user data</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"></span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"参考来源\">参考来源</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SOCKS\">SOCKS(维基百科)</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://my.oschina.net/997155658/blog/1563154\">SOCKS5 协议介绍</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1928\">rfc1928</a></p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[{"id":"